txt.en: You have helped the March on Gundabad fight back against the Angmarim influence in Elderslade.
You have slain many dragons during your time in Elderslade. The March on Gundabad has recognized your efforts.
Many Orcs have fallen before you, helping secure Elderslade for the March on Gundabad.
Defeat many enemies hostile to the March on Gundabad.
The threat of the hobgoblins in Elderslade has diminished, aiding the March on Gundabad.
Thanks to your efforts, the trolls of Elderslade do not have the numbers to threaten the March on Gundabad as much.
Fewer Wargs roam the hills of Elderslade, and for that, the March on Gundabad is grateful.
Defeat many enemies hostile to the March on Gundabad.
